### 7. **Client Generator TS Implementation**
**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775389229566-n145p2/packages/client-generator-ts/src/generator.ts`

