### 8. **Minimal Generator Example** (Test)
**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775389229566-n145p2/packages/generator-helper/src/__tests__/minimal-executable`

